Params: {3: 'After checking multiple times, you push open the door before you.'}
{3: 'Just like the numerous doors you have already opened, the scene behind this door makes no sense at all from an architectural perspective.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "When I'm back to reality, I will probably be disappointed if I don't see a ruin after opening a door.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "Indeed. We have seen too many abnormal things behind those doors. I won't blame you if you are disappointed after seeing normal scenes.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "Is that M.I.N.D. deviation...? I'll book a calibration for us after we go back.", 4: '3'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Let's end this. My sensor is going to get faulty if I stay in this environment for too long.", 4: '3'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Ayla', 3: 'Yeah, the movie is ending soon. This is the last battle.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Ayla', 3: 'Destroy the only Book of Death, and the memory spaces will lose their foundation.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Narration', 3: 'With this final determination, you step into the strange doorâ€”'}
